title: Raspberry Pi The Complete Manual - 2014  UK
description:
Raspberry Pi The Complete Manual - 2014  UK

148 Pages | True PDF | English | 14 MB 


Since its launch, the Raspberry Pi has taken the world by storm. It has provided a much-needed impetus to students in the classroom by helping them overcome their fear of programming and coding, while assisting adults to create some extremely unique small and large-scale projects that have got the entire community excited. This complete manual contains everything you need to know to get started with your Raspberry Pi and then follow the incredible projects within.
